data.description: Like new home in desirable Hannah Ridge built in 2020!  Close to great shopping and easy drive to all military bases! Enter via the welcoming porch to wide plank flooring and new carpet on the main and upper levels!  Front office with French doors makes working from home a breeze!  The kitchen and family room have space for easy living and large gatherings!  Huge granite island and many many cabinets!  Upgraded stainless steel appliances and gas stove!  The kitchen opens to a large dining area and extends back to two, yes, two walk in pantries and a dream mud room with bench, desk, cabinets and shelves.  A cubby for every person and place to pay the bills or do homework!  Upstairs is a very large loft with peek-a-boo views gives room for a third family room and movie time!  The private master retreat is so spacious and relaxing you won't want to leave!  Your private master bedroom deck for morning coffee and an evening glass of wine!  What a wonderful way to live!  Three large bedrooms upstairs and a full bath with separate shower/toilet area make mornings easy!  Upstairs laundry with lower cabinets and folding counter!  The full finished basement has two more spaces for entertaining or family time and another large bedroom, a full bath and finished storage (the carpet will be put down in the storage room before closing.)  Spacious private back yard with gorgeous grass and extended patio that wraps around the house!  Concrete walk to gate as well!  Raised bed garden is ready to go!  Exterior furniture can be purchased separately!  Three car tandem garage gives space for the large vehicles and storage!   Green spaces and parks in the neighborhood! You are going to love living here!
